{
  "stem": "15576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got, every month, a package, like this, here, from my aunt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- there-- there are some very good articles there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were romances that were going for months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "God forbid, a paper should get lost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another thing I didn't mention, we had no-- did I mention, we had no electricity?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to steal a lamp and climb up in the attic and read.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved to read.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was then, just-- you know, our house was an old-fashioned house, with bricks, but with a straw roof.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- I mean from the movies, from the other movies you'll see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no-- no way you could go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't go from Russia to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just-- just-- My father, I think, was trying, yes, before where we had letters from our father, every single week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every single week, we had letters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I imagine it was much harder for-- you know, with kids, they play this, and they forget.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my mother, I don't remember her ever smiling from that point, from there on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was-- as a matter of fact, I have all the letters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father saved every letter from my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I found out a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From one letter, she mentions you-- you're OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have your family there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have your aunt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was your aunt's fault.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Your-- your aunt-- your sister, rather, should have tried a little bit harder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know my-- the uncle was busy with business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you should have tried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She should have tried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Letters like this, so I got the feeling how mother felt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's a-- it was a very emotional, hard time for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
